name: TimingGroups

properties.name: length
properties.description: The number of objects in the collection.

parameters.name: dynamicTarget
parameters.description: A page item target that is an animation, media, or mso. Can accept: PageItem, Graphic, Behavior or MediaItem.
The time delay in seconds for a target. (Optional)
parameters.name: delaySeconds
withProperties
parameters.description: Initial values for properties of the new TimingGroup (Optional)

methods.name: count
methods.description: Displays the number of elements in the TimingGroup.

methods.name: item
methods.description: Returns the TimingGroup with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

methods.name: itemByRange
methods.description: Returns the TimingGroups within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: The TimingGroup, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: TimingGroup, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: The TimingGroup, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: TimingGroup, Long Integer or String.

methods.name: firstItem
methods.description: Returns the first TimingGroup in the collection.

methods.name: lastItem
methods.description: Returns the last TimingGroup in the collection.

methods.name: middleItem
methods.description: Returns the middle TimingGroup in the collection.

methods.name: previousItem
methods.description: Returns the TimingGroup with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The index of the TimingGroup that follows the desired TimingGroup.

methods.name: nextItem
methods.description: Returns the TimingGroup whose index follows the specified TimingGroup in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.description: The TimingGroup whose index comes before the desired TimingGroup.

methods.name: anyItem
methods.description: Returns any TimingGroup in the collection.

methods.name: everyItem
methods.description: Returns every TimingGroup in the collection.

methods.name: toSource
methods.description: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the TimingGroup.
Returns the TimingGroup with the specified index.

description: A collection of timing data objects.
